languages.en: //[DIANA]\\//(0,30)\\Ljudmila Vetrova can be found in the public sections of the island, primarily tending to client needs.

languages.es: //[DIANA]\\//(0,2.643943)\\Encontrarás a Ljudmila Vetrova en las secciones//(2.643943,4.2779)\\públicas de la isla,//(4.2779,7.057187)\\donde estará atendiendo a los clientes.
